<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT-Hutchinson raised to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Hutchinson raised to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>--Dain Bosworth Inc said Monday it raised Hutchinson Technology Inc to buy from hold and raised its fiscal 1997 earnings estimate on the company to $3.28 a share from $2.67.</p>
<p>--Developments in the company's Trace Suspension Assembly high-performance suspension technology should provide long-term growth, while strong demand for computer disk drive suspensions should allow the company to maintain healthy average selling prices and gross margins in the near term, Dain Bosworth said.</p>
<p>--Hutchinson shares were down 5/8 at 35-1/4 Monday.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
